SnowBlozm 
PHP Service Architecture and Workflow Framework
http://snowblozm.blogspot.com/

Simplified Service Oriented Architecture
Vibhaj Rajan
vibhaj8@gmail.com

Features 
	Experimental Service Computing Platform for managing services and workflows
	Reference Structure for managing entities
	Key-Chain-Web Mechanism for access control
	Integrated Application Layer Security for access security

